arStrings.szText: Your Healing Potion no longer Heals instantly, instead it grants a {c_important}{u}Barrier{/u}{/c} for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 1"|%|]{/c} of the healing for {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds. While you have a {c_important}{u}Barrier{/u}{/c}, you gain {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|%|]{/c} Damage Reduction.
